## Role Hierarchy Reference

Each role level inherits from the level below:

```
ADMIN → CREATE → WRITE → READ
                            ↑
RBAC ────────────────────────┘ (separate branch)
```

Granting a user `WRITE` also provides `READ` access automatically.

## Verification

After applying grants, run the verification query to confirm:
- Each user has their assigned role
- No users have roles above their authorized level
- Inherited roles are visible in the hierarchy

